        <p>Read <u>Helen&rsquo;s Plan</u>.&nbsp; The narrative pretty much explains how she with the help of family, friends and neighbors <strong>created a plan</strong> that works for leaving your home for short periods of time.&nbsp; Helen&rsquo;s Plan also addresses how to <strong>make a kit</strong>.</p>
        <p>Also, read the brochure titled <u>Preparing makes sense for Older Pennsylvanians</u>.&nbsp; It will help you with your Plan and your Kit.</p>
