        <p><u>Caution:</u>&nbsp; the PEPG and the Brochure for Older Pennsylvanians recommends creating a Home Emergency Kit. This involves far too many times needed for a short term evacuation.&nbsp; Follow Helen&rsquo;s Plan for short term evacuations;&nbsp; the PEPG and Older Pennsylvanians kits are more appropriate for Sheltering in Place.</p>
        <p><u>Remember</u> to always keep your vehicle&rsquo;s fuel tank or batteries &ldquo;full&rdquo;,&nbsp; and keep your mobile phone and laptop fully charged.</p>
